 {"id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "title": "Implement minimal net plus app/CLI/doctor integration for the core runtime", "description": "Implement the minimal net/app integration layer needed to use the runtime in realistic workflows: basic DNS/TCP/UDP style primitives where appropriate, plus CLI/app/doctor entrypoints that expose deterministic run/replay/diagnostics.", "design": "Scope includes:
- minimal network surface sufficient for “core” workflows rather than full HTTP stack parity,
- app/bootstrap/doctor/run entrypoints,
- structured output/progress/diagnostic plumbing.", "acceptance_criteria": "A. A user can stand up and inspect realistic runtime workflows through supported entrypoints.
B. Minimal net primitives are integrated with the runtime model rather than being external helpers.
C. CLI/doctor/app surfaces are documented/tested enough to support parity work and demos.
D. The implementation ships with comprehensive module-level unit tests, invariant or law-style tests where applicable, and at least one logged end-to-end or lab scenario that emits structured evidence artifacts and high-signal diagnostics.", "notes": "This remains deliberately below full transport-stack parity; the goal is usable core integration, not yet HTTP/gRPC completeness.", "status": "closed", "priority": 3, "issue_type": "task", "created_at": "2026-03-12T16:53:49.435253377Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "updated_at": "2026-03-12T22:55:29.506614572Z", "closed_at": "2026-03-12T22:55:29.505341852Z", "source_repo": ".", "compaction_level": 0, "original_size": 0, "labels": ["app", "core-parity", "doctor", "net"], "dependencies": [{"issue_id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "depends_on_id": "bd-1eqo.2.2", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-12T17:12:41.396905608Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "depends_on_id": "bd-1eqo.2.6", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-12T17:28:12.318388644Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "depends_on_id": "bd-1eqo.4.3", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-12T17:12:47.918763898Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "depends_on_id": "bd-1eqo.8.1", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-12T16:55:00.194134308Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "depends_on_id": "bd-1eqo.9", "type": "parent-child", "created_at": "2026-03-12T16:53:49.435253377Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}, {"issue_id": "bd-1eqo.9.2", "depends_on_id": "bd-1eqo.9.1", "type": "blocks", "created_at": "2026-03-12T16:54:59.339864712Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "metadata": "{}", "thread_id": ""}], "close_reason": "Completed. Evidence: tests/e2e/e2e_network_surface.c, tests/unit/app/test_app.c, tests/unit/cli/test_cli.c, tests/unit/net/